ul&amp;author=A+Kamali+Polat&amp;author=K+Aslan&amp;publication_year=2014&amp;journal=Ulus+Travma+Acil+Cerrahi+Derg&amp;pages=417-422&amp;doi=10.5505%2Ftjtes.2014.52959&amp;pmid=25541920">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">15.</div><div id="r15" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Stuhlfaut JW, Anderson SW, Soto JA. Blunt abdominal trauma: current imaging techniques and CT findings in patients with solid organ, bowel, and mesenteric injury. <em>Semin Ultrasound CT MR</em> 2007;28(2):115–129.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1053/j.sult.2007.01.004">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17432766/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Blunt+abdominal+trauma%3A+current+imaging+techniques+and+CT+findings+in+patients+with+solid+organ%2C+bowel%2C+and+mesenteric+injury&amp;author=JW+Stuhlfaut&amp;author=SW+Anderson&amp;author=JA+Soto&amp;publication_year=2007&amp;journal=Semin+Ultrasound+CT+MR&amp;pages=115-129&amp;doi=10.1053%2Fj.sult.2007.01.004&amp;pmid=17432766">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">16.</div><div id="r16" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Lee CH, Haaland B, Earnest A, Tan CH. Use of positive oral contrast agents in abdominopelvic computed tomography for blunt abdominal injury: meta-analysis and systematic review. <em>Eur Radiol</em> 2013;23(9):2513–2521.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00330-013-2860-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/23624596/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/schola